column5: Anyone know of a drive in camp in NW Ontario near Kenora, Minaki, Ear Falls, LOTW thats got availability? 7 guys may not be able to get into WCPP due to fires and looking for plan B. Thanks in advance!!
Wine Lake has a cabin on Wabaskang that might be open during that time. It is in Perrault Falls and it is a drive to cabin.
Paradise Cove in Minaki usually has openings and is good fishing this time of year
Just checked with Marcel at Birch Dale Lodge on Eagle Lake 807-227-5262 www,birchdalelodge.com, he has an opening, give him a call.
We have a opening and are willing to work with you as such if not able to go to your booked place Give us a call anytime 807 727 2384
YES!! Thank you all! We're hoping for the best getting into WCPP but as of now we're smoked out in need of ideas for plan B. Thanks again,
